Npcyell_18831_Text: All right, it's time to reinforce this area of the base! When we're done, it'll be safer and more cosmotastic than ever before!
Npcyell_18832_Text: Keep a careful eye on the glass foundation, but don't let our other work fall by the wayside!
Npcyell_18994_Text: Work is progressing better than I could've imagined! Keep up the pace!
Npcyell_18995_Text: We're only a hop, skip, and a jump away from our goal! One final pushâ”€for the initiative!
Npcyell_19023_Text: With this, we should be able to pave the way! Thank you all for your cooperation!
Npcyell_19025_Text: This elegant design, complete with a masterful implementation of glass, will surely grab the attention of one and all. I commend your passionate work!
Npcyell_19026_Text: With this, I'm sure we can expect even better results from our mech ops in the future! Rest now, my friends, and hop back here to see the finished result later!
Npcyell_19033_Text: Excellent work, everyone! A few more finishing touches, and our drones should feel right at home.
Npcyell_19034_Text: While our next mission relies heavily on their performance, we will still require help from contributors like you. Rest up while you have the chance!
Npcyell_19035_Text: The glass seems to be cooling nicely! Its color and appearance should change any moment now...
Npcyell_19036_Text: In the meantime, be sure to cool down, heat up, or otherwise achieve your desired body temperature. We shall continue our campaign shortly.
Npcyell_19037_Text: And the rest, we shall leave to the drones! Thank you for making Operation Chilling-a-Way a phenomenal success!
Npcyell_19038_Text: Now nothing can stop us from exploring every nook and cranny on Phaenna! ...But perhaps we should break for a carroty beverage first.
